com.goinstant.auth
Interface User

All Known Implementing Classes:
PlainUser
public interface User

Defines properties of a User in GoInstant. For more information on users, please see the GoInstant guide on Users And Authentication See PlainUser for a concrete implementation.

getID

String getID()
Unique, permanent ID for this user. Numeric IDs make good permanent identifiers. Usernames and email addresses not so much, since they're liable to change.
